{"tid":541227,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"突發：Apple Watch Series 3配合網絡功能快來港了！　　Csl Mobile率先支援","createTime":"2018-01-26T08:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T09:23:05.000Z","uid":23677,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"ca55192036c992d8bfa6956aaf6f34ed50241d6b","tid":541227,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:10:20.000Z","msg":"Apple Watch Series 3在發佈時，香港沒有包括在內，反而由大陸行先。蘋果如今終於照顧一下香港用戶，Apple Watch Series 3配合網絡功能將於2月2日起接受訂購，並會在2月9日起發售。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然智能手錶在香港不算是熱潮，但香港的csl Mobile似乎對此頗有信心，就在香港蘋果發佈有關消息後，他們也表示將會是首間支援eSIM的電訊商，屆時用家就算只配戴Apple Watch，沒有iPhone或iPad配合也好，亦能使用當中的上網功能。<br />\n<br />\n至於售價方面，從香港蘋果官方網站可以看到，有網絡功能的Apple Watch Series 3售價為HK$3188起。<br />\n<br />\ncsl Mobile發出的官方新聞稿如下：<br />\n<br />\nCSL Mobile率先在港推出Apple Watch Series 3（GPS + Cellular）<br />\n即日起接受訂購<br />\ncsl及1O1O客戶可免費連接eSIM<br />\n<br />\n香港電訊（股份代號：6823）【香港．2018年1月26日】 ─ csl及1O1O今天宣佈，將於2018年2月9日起開始發售Apple Watch Series 3 （GPS + Cellular），為全球最受歡迎的Apple Watch加入內置流動網絡功能。<br />\n<br />\n透過流動網絡，客戶只需隨身攜帶Apple Watch，便可與人保持緊密聯繫及接收信息。為了幫助客戶開始使用Apple Watch Series 3（GPS + Cellular），csl及1O1O客戶將可免費連接eSIM。<br />\n<br />\n要啟動Apple Watch Series 3（GPS + Cellular）的流動通訊服務，客戶首先需更新iPhone至iOS 11.2.5版本，然後點擊設定&gt;一般&gt;關於本機，及按照提示更新至最新電訊商設定。<br />\n<br />\n有關收費及服務計劃詳情，<a href=\"http://請瀏覽網頁www.hkcsl.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%AB%8B%E7%80%8F%E8%A6%BD%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81www.hkcsl.com&d=PKFOq%2F3hdZkIocf411TDxGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=2836191e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">請瀏覽網頁www.hkcsl.com</a> 或 <a href=\"http://www.1010.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.1010.com.hk&d=PKFOq%2F3hdZkIocf411TDxGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=ff94e926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.1010.com.hk</a>。<br />\n<br />\n有關iPhone及Apple Watch詳情，<a href=\"http://請瀏覽網站www.apple.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%AB%8B%E7%80%8F%E8%A6%BD%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.apple.com&d=PKFOq%2F3hdZkIocf411TDxGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=1e46de5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">請瀏覽網站www.apple.com</a>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2018/01/apple-watch-series-3-csl-mobile/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2018%2F01%2Fapple-watch-series-3-csl-mobile%2F&d=PKFOq%2F3hdZkIocf411TDxGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=83dc0506\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2018/01/apple-watch-series-3-csl-mobile/</a>"},{"pid":"2f33ea03db95dde2fddc63f0551c64e88dca8f3d","tid":541227,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"支那個sSIM功能唔係被禁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487a22e386680094b8be200162d877babd48db81","tid":541227,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"月費點計？"},{"pid":"76f252823462b47e5799eace46d2466abe51a235","tid":541227,"uid":47377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"487a22e386680094b8be200162d877babd48db81","tid":541227,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"月費點計？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:20:29.000Z","msg":"內文更新咗<br />\n<br />\n至於售價方面，從香港蘋果官方網站可以看到，有網絡功能的Apple Watch Series 3售價為HK$3188起。csl回應winandmac Media查詢時，指「csl及1O1O客戶將可免費連接eSIM，即不用加錢。」"},{"pid":"1d19ea642b8a4ce70224b1f748ce0889b126fe01","tid":541227,"uid":2613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f33ea03db95dde2fddc63f0551c64e88dca8f3d","tid":541227,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"支那個sSIM功能唔係被禁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:44:51.000Z","msg":"已經賣返啦<br />\n預計今年內出牌"},{"pid":"28e3711ee60ecac47420c92529cfe9015e72d19d","tid":541227,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:53:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd41987